text: "Rooster" is a 1993 song by Alice in Chains and is the fourth single from their second studio album Dirt. It went to number 35 in Hungary and number 7 on the Billboard Mainstream Rock chart. It was later included on their 2006 greatest hits album The Essential Alice in Chains. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:1993 songs Category:1990s ballads Category:Alice in Chains songs Category:Alternative rock songs Category:Heavy metal
